description:
Create a rustic feel in your dining room or eat-in kitchen with these wood dining chairs full of country charm. Built from solid wood and wood veneer for remarkable strength and durability, these farmhouse-style dining chairs fit nicely in rustic or country decor. The wide slat backs of these chairs support your body as you sit, and the dark oak finish blends seamlessly with other wood furniture in your room.
